   <text>
      <body>
         <div type="translation">
            <ab>Athenodoros to Poseidonios and Demetria, greeting. If you and the children are healthy, it is as I want. I myself am healthy as well. If Heliodoros has not yet sent you Ö (here the papyrus breaks off.) (On the verso) To Poseidonios and Demetria Ö from Athenodoros.</ab>
         </div>
